💚 I am so thankful for my mum👩‍👧. A candle🕯 can keep a room glow with its light, but a mum like her makes all my days bright!💡🌞 My mum 👩‍🦰 inspired me to dream God-sized💥 dreams, speaks truth & encouragement in difficult seasons & reminds me how I shine🌟. She has made a difference in my life greatly 😇 .
Mothers are incredible creation of God 😇. My mum spent her life pouring selflessly & sacrificially into me. When I was young 👶👧, she carried diaper bags, waterbottles, lunchboxes,🎒, books & bandages. When I grew up👩, she gracefully carry all my burdens, worries, cares & concerns! .
Being a mom is like no other job in the world & her job is never done. Unlike a typical 9-to-5 job, motherhood is a “career” often motivated by pure & unwavering 🔥love. Mum cares & nurtures me.🎋 She knows me deeply & loves me dearly, all the while instilling the importance of a love, empathy & compassion for others. She takes her role seriously, praying for me, guiding me & serving me as a beautiful reflection of God’s unfailing & unrelenting love. .
👩‍🦰 Mum, words can’t explain how I feel. I appreciate your presence & existence. Who you are is irreplaceable. You’re an awesome mother🦸‍♀️ You’re a virtuous wife 👨‍👩‍👧 You're a gift of love that fills my heart & my life. I’m so grateful for all that you poured into me. You showed me what love feels like & made me believe I could take on the world. You always saw the best in me & hoped the best for me. You were selfless over & over & over again. I wouldn’t be here without you! I would be so lost without you! Thank you from the bottom of my heart. I’m so privileged to call you, "Mom"!🌹

"A rose by any other name would smell as sweet" ~ Shakespeare

Answer: 10 times 🙋‍♀️ My mom is the best thing I could ever ask for. She is the most supportive and most loving mom out there. ❤️ I never knew how much she sacrificed and how much she had done for me all these years before I became a mother myself.  She had to bring up 5 kids all by herself. Those though times were hard and we did not have much money, but she was a great mom and took care of us all very well. I didn’t know how difficult it is to be a mom but now I totally feel it and experience it firsthand for myself.  Being a mom definitely is not an easy job. Yet she never complained or made a sound. It was all love and smiles. I really want to be like a mom her but I find it very hard. She is a perfect mom. I can never say enough or ever express fully in words on how much I love her and show how great she is❤. Mother's Day is meant to make mothers happy and show great appreciation to our mothers. ❤ My mom loves shopping . This giveaway is perfect for my dearest mom. I am sure she will be very happy if I can win this gift for her. She is a great mom and she deserves to have the best. 💯🥇 @wheelockplace @momo_album @ic_life8 @friendly_kat

10 times. @wheelockplace @chongmehong @ginkhoo @eileen.loo.54 
慈 母 手 中 线，
游 子 身 上 衣。
临 行 密 密 缝，
意 恐 迟 迟 归。
谁 言 寸 草 心，
报 得 三 春 晖。

This poetry expresses how wonderful my mother is. To me, she is a good chef. Her love & knowledge have no expiry date. Her smiles and hugs are there whenever I need, There's no need heating up, it's always warm and fresh! Her care and concern that she gave me, I will not worry that I will put on weight. All is healthy food with fruits & vegetables!

Her patience & strength is constantly available like the salt and spices needed in a pot of delicious soup. She used low heat mode for boiling the tonic double boil soup to teach me to be resilient and stay persistent until I succeed. We talk everything under the sun; our relationship gets closer than before. Don’t you agree?

I'm grabbing this superb opportunity now to say proudly – Mummy, I love you more than words can express! She always put our needs before her and very stingy on herself. She deserve to be pampered with full of love!!! 💕💕 Happy Mother's Day to all the mothers!! 谢谢你,您辛苦了!!

10 times in various languages 

Looking forward to be one of the lucky winners so that I can show my appreciation and bring my mom to @wheelockplace which is known to be an exciting cosmopolitan destination that meets every demand of the stylish urbanite.

Wishing all mums a Happy Mother’s Day!

@wheelockplace @inoran_81 @tansharon6783  @hkse88

10 times! @wheelockplace @wwjypiglet @rainbowstairways @fullof567
I hope to win and surprise my mum as she is my role model! While I am growing up, she was down with cancer twice but she never give up on life no matter how tough it might be! When the going get tough, the tough get going, that's what she always believes in. She inspires and influences me to be a stronger individual! 
Here a heartfelt message for this iron lady in my heart:
You are as compassionate as an angel,
Who guided me out of darkness,
You ignited the sparks in me and drive me out of sadness!
My dearest mum, it is your unconditional love that help me recovered from sadness when things were not going their way.
You are the one who hold my hand, when others walk away!
You are the one who dry my tears and show me the way!
You make me believe that the light is at the end of the tunnel, when I lost my way!
You are our angel, my sunshine, my everything! 
Without you, I will not be what I am today.
10 times the word 'Mom' appeared in different languages @wheelockplace @eatwatchexperience @iilikeshopping @mymummydoesntliketocook

10 times @wheelockplace @dragon_chenlong @m.elann.e @alvinkohcl14 
My mum is special to me simply because she is my first love, the first woman I'm in love with and yet afraid of her at the same time! 😆 This feeling is indescribable! Hope to win this for her, she will be very happy! 
Last but not least,
Here is a heartfelt message for her: 
You make me everything I am.
Thank you for taking the time,
Thank you for showing me the way,
And thank you for being there when I need you,
Thank you for every single day.
Thank you for your guiding hand,
Thank you for making my dreams come true,
You're an extraordinary woman,
And I hope you're as proud of me
As I am proud of you.
Thank you for giving me life,
Thank you for showing me good from bad! 
Thank you for all your contributions to the family,
Thank you for being my Mum.
I love you, and I always have!
Happy Mother's day to my dearest mum!
